description:
If the dollar price (exchange rate) of one euro (EUR) is below $1.0000 on August 31, 2022 (according to the "Price" column on investing.com), this market will resolve to "Yes". Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market is the EUR/USD currency exchange rate found on investing.com, specifically the historical daily "Price" column: https://www.investing.com/currencies/eur-usd-historical-data. If the resolution source is unavailable at the resolution time, other credible reporting may be used.

This market may resolve only after the "Price" for August 31, 2022, on the "EUR/USD Historical Data" chart is finalized. If for any reason (e.g. market holiday, emergency market closure) there is no "Price" on that chart for this market's resolution date, the "Price" of the nearest previous date will be used.
